obert Lenveise于1120年出生在英国越可爾爾姆斯利。她于1136年与Robert de Lenveise结婚。他们至少是1个儿子的父母。她去世于1136年在英国貝德福爾比格萊斯瓦德享年16岁。"},"hr":{"1120–1136":"1120.–1136.","1115–1136":"1115–1136.","1136–1166":"1136.–1166","1115":"1115","1136":"1136.","1166":"1166","1120":"1120.","Ros, Helmsley, North Yorkshire, England":"Helmsley, Yorkshire, England","Laxton, Northamptonshire, England":"Laxton, Northamptonshire, Engleska, United Kingdom","Biggleswade, Bedfordshire, England":"Biggleswade, Bedfordshire, England"},"cs":{"1120–1136":"1120–1136","1115–1136":"1115–1136","1136–1166":"1136–1166","1115":"1115","1136":"1136","1166":"1166","1120":"1120","Ros, Helmsley, North Yorkshire, England":"Helmsley, Yorkshire, Anglie","Laxton, Northamptonshire, England":"Laxton, Northamptonshire, Anglie, United Kingdom","Biggleswade, Bedfordshire, England":"Biggleswade, Bedfordshire, Anglie"},"da":{"1120–1136":"1120–1136","1115–1136":"1115–1136","1136–1166":"1136–1166","1115":"1115","1136":"1136","1166":"1166","1120":"1120","Ros, Helmsley, North Yorkshire, England":"Helmsley, Jórvík, England","Laxton, Northamptonshire, England":"Laxton, Northamptonshire, England, United Kingdom","Biggleswade, Bedfordshire, England":"Biggleswade, Bedfordshire, England"},"nl":{"1120–1136":"1120–1136","1115–1136":"1115–1136","1136–1166":"1136–1166","1115":"1115","1136":"1136","1166":"1166","1120":"1120","Ros, Helmsley, North Yorkshire, England":"Helmsley, Yorkshire, England","Laxton, Northamptonshire, England":"Laxton, Northamptonshire, Engeland, Verenigd Koninkrijk","Biggleswade, Bedfordshire, England":"Biggleswade, Bedfordshire, England"},"en":{"1120–1136":"1120–1136","1115–1136":"1115–1136","1136–1166":"1136–1166","1115":"1115","1136":"1136","1166":"1166","1120":"1120","Ros, Helmsley, North Yorkshire, England":"Helmsley, Yorkshire, England","Laxton, Northamptonshire, England":"Laxton, Northamptonshire, England, United Kingdom","Biggleswade, Bedfordshire, England":"Biggleswade, Bedfordshire, England","nameMeanings":[{"name":"Robert","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["One of the many French names of Germanic origin that were introduced into Britain by the Normans; it has since remained in continuous use. It is derived from the nearly synonymous elements <i>hrōd</i> ‘fame’ + <i>berht</i> ‘bright, famous’, and had a native Old English predecessor of similar form (<i>Hreodbeorht</i>), which was supplanted by the Norman name. Two dukes of Normandy in the 11th century bore the name: the father of  William the Conqueror  (sometimes identified with the legendary Robert the Devil), and his eldest son. It was borne also by three kings of Scotland, notably  Robert the Bruce  (  1274–1329 ), who freed Scotland from English domination. The altered short form <i>Bob</i> is very common, but <i>Hob</i> and <i>Dob</i>, which were common in the Middle Ages and gave rise to surnames, are extinct.  See also  Rupert ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Mrs Robert Lenveise was born in 1120, in Helmsley, Yorkshire, England. She married Robert de Lenveise in 1136. They were the parents of at least 1 son. She died in 1136, in Biggleswade, Bedfordshire, England, at the age of 16."},"et":{"1120–1136":"1120–1136","1115–1136":"1115–1136","1136–1166":"1136–1166","1115":"1115","1136":"1136","1166":"1166","1120":"1120","Ros, Helmsley, North Yorkshire, England":"Helmsley, Yorkshire, England","Laxton, Northamptonshire, England":"Laxton, Northamptonshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Biggleswade, Bedfordshire, England":"Biggleswade, Bedfordshire, England"},"fi":{"1120–1136":"1120–1136","1115–1136":"1115–1136","1136–1166":"1136–1166","1115":"1115","1136":"1136","1166":"1166","1120":"1120","Ros, Helmsley, North Yorkshire, England":"Helmsley, Yorkshire, England","Laxton, Northamptonshire, England":"Laxton, Northamptonshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Biggleswade, Bedfordshire, England":"Biggleswade, Bedfordshire, England"},"fr":{"1120–1136":"11